<view class="scaffold-screen">
  <view class="scaffold-header">
    <text class="scaffold-kicker">Local route contract</text>
    <text class="scaffold-title">{{title}}</text>
    <text class="scaffold-subtitle">启动页只展示本地壳、API 和数据库读回契约，不声明任何像素参考。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="contract-card">
    <view class="contract-icon api"></view>
    <view class="contract-copy">
      <text class="contract-title">/api/scaffold/ping</text>
      <text class="contract-desc">返回 local adapter status</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="contract-card">
    <view class="contract-icon db"></view>
    <view class="contract-copy">
      <text class="contract-title">/api/scaffold/db-readback</text>
      <text class="contract-desc">写入并读回 diagnosis_orders</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="contract-note">
    <text>该页面是路由与契约可见性页面，不是 UI 参考屏或截图挂载页。</text>
  </view>

  <button class="scaffold-enter" data-action="home" bindtap="onTap">进入首页</button>
</view>
